Description:
Agreement with Citibank N.A. dated 10/21/2005 to pay 5.46% times the notional amount per year. In exchange for that periodic payment, upon a default by Toys 'R' Us, Inc., Citibank N.A. agrees to pay the Portfolio the notional amount of the swap. To receive that payment, the
 Portfolio must deliver a bond (with par value equal to the notional amount of the swap) issued by Toys 'R' Us, Inc. to Citibank N.A.
